data.description: New pricing! Looking for a home with a NEW ROOF? This charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home with a 2 car garage may be just what you are looking for! Located on the East side of South Venice, This home features a windowed enclosed Florida room, Hurricane protection for all windows, Updated Kitchen with solid surface counters, an open floor plan that's sure to please! The wide driveway is perfect for a boat or extra "toys". This is a quiet neighborhood with easy access to US41 at a traffic light.  Split bedroom Plan. Optional HOA access to the South Venice Beach, Ferry. and boat launch! Just a few minute drive to Historic Downtown Venice with shops and restaurants galore. Beaches in all directions! Downtown Wellen Park is just about 15 minutes away with the Atlanta Braves winter ballpark and shops, restaurants and entertainment! Don' hesitate to come see this home soon!
